South African Efforts to Spur New Growth Trajectory, Finance Minister Says

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-04-14T05:03:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-14/south-african-efforts-to-spur-new-growth-trajectory-finance-minister-says.html
South African Finance Minister
 Pravin Gordhan  said efforts by the country’s government will
help remove obstacles and put the country on a “much more
favorable growth trajectory.”  He made the comments in an interview published in the Wall
Street Journal.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  